           <li class="directory-item text whats-new"> <h3><a href="//aws.amazon.com/about-aws/whats-new/2019/07/now-use-aws-systems-manager-maintenance-windows-to-select-resource-groups-as-targets/">Now use AWS Systems Manager Maintenance Windows to select resource groups as targets</a></h3> 
            <div class="date">
